<div class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center vh-100">
  <div class="card p-4 mt-4 mw-100 mb-4" style="width: 900px; max-height: 85vh; overflow-y: auto;">

    {{#if message}}
    <div class="alert alert-danger text-center">
      {{message}}
    </div>
    {{/if}}

    <div class="d-flex flex-row">
      <div class="p-2">
        <p style="font-size: x-large;">Welcome to Spot Drop!</p>
        <p class ="para-text" style="font-size: smaller;">Spot Drop was built by action sports enthusiasts, for action sports enthusiasts. Whether you're a skater, snowboarder, climber, freeskier, or parkour runner. we know the feeling of wasting time looking for a good spot, so we built something to fix that.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: x-large">What we do</p>
        <p class="para-text" style="font-size: smaller;">Spot Drop is a community-driven spot locator for anyone who pushes the limits of what's possible outdoors and in the streets. Find hidden gems near you, share your favorite spots with the community, and never waste a session again. Whether you're hunting for a smooth ledge in the city, a powder stash off the beaten path, a sick bouldering route, or the perfect rooftop run. Spot Drop has you covered.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: x-large">Why we built it</p>
        <p class="para-text" style="font-size: smaller;">The best spots are always passed down through word of mouth, a friend of a friend who knows a guy. We wanted to put all of that local knowledge in one place and make it available to everyone. No gatekeeping, just good spots!
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: x-large">Join the community</p>
        <p class="para-text" style="font-size: smaller;">
          Drop a spot. Leave a comment. Help someone find their next favorite session. Spot Drop grows with every user who contributes, so get out there and add your local spots to the map.
        </p>
      </div>
      <img class = "about-img" src="../../resources/img/Spot Drop Logo Vertical.svg" alt="SpotDrop Logo">

    </div>


  </div>
</div>